title: Martin Hayes and Dennis Cahill - Live In Seattle
description:
Artist: Martin Hayes and Dennis Cahill
Album: Live In Seattle
Year: 1999
Produced by: Green Linnet

This album was recorded directly from original CD to a Variable bit rate MP3 format of 224Kbps. The second track is particularly memorable.
